# Release/ carries the game content tmServer loads at boot (W2PP_CONTENT: rates,
# catalogs, BaseMob templates, serv00.htm, maps), so it must stay in the build
# context — but drop the heavyweight legacy build/debug artifacts we never read
# (MSVC symbols, incremental-link files, the legacy binaries, a 4.6 MB test dump).
